{"type":"turn_end","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have enough information to make my decision. Based on my careful review of the arbitration record and admitted evidence, I can see that the key issue revolves around whether the U.S. military operation in Venezuela qualifies under the proposition's specific criteria.\n\nThe proposition requires U.S. ground forces to enter Venezuelan territory in combat capacity with the objective of:\n1. Seizing or holding territory, OR\n2. Removing the sitting government, OR  \n3. Establishing operational control of a major population center\n\nThe evidence shows:\n- U.S. ground forces did enter Caracas (ground-based extraction force)\n- The operation occurred before the January 31, 2026 expiration\n- Maduro was removed from power\n\nHowever, the critical issue is the objective. The official sources consistently characterize this as a \"raid,\" \"capture,\" \"extraction,\" and \"arrest\" mission - not an invasion or extended military operation. The proposition specifically excludes \"capture of a head of state without territorial occupation\" and \"special operations raids without territorial objectives.\"\n\nWhile Maduro was removed from power, the evidence does not establish that the objective was territorial occupation or operational control of Caracas. The U.S. oversight described appears to be political influence rather than military control.\n\nBased on the preponderance of evidence standard and the specific exclusions in the proposition, I find that the plaintiff has not demonstrated that this operation meets the qualifying criteria."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d50b","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"not_demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The official sources characterize the operation as a raid/capture/extraction mission, not territorial occupation or operational control. The proposition specifically excludes capture of a head of state without territorial occupation and special operations raids without territorial objectives. While U.S. ground forces entered Caracas and Maduro was removed, the evidence does not establish the qualifying territorial or governmental-control objective required by the proposition.\"}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":226,"output":402,"cacheRead":45248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45876,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782784294803,"responseId":"gen-1782784295-PmScrmy02sVg7Q8STXZN"},"toolResults":[{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d50b","toolName":"mcp","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C1\ncase_id: arb-ex06-20260630013224\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C1\nremaining_ms: 750461\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex06-20260630013224\",\"member_id\":\"C1\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"text\":\"Council vote accepted.\"},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":true,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-30T02:04:10.33535468Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C1\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C1\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":750461,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_number\":9}}"}],"details":{"mode":"call","mcpResult":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C1\ncase_id: arb-ex06-20260630013224\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C1\nremaining_ms: 750461\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex06-20260630013224\",\"member_id\":\"C1\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"text\":\"Council vote accepted.\"},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":true,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-30T02:04:10.33535468Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C1\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C1\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":750461,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_number\":9}}"}],"structuredContent":{"case_id":"arb-ex06-20260630013224","member_id":"C1","ok":true,"result":{"text":"Council vote accepted."},"turn":{"attempts_max":3,"attempts_remaining":3,"completed":true,"deadline":"2026-06-30T02:04:10.33535468Z","deliberation_round":1,"member_id":"C1","opportunity_id":"deliberation:1:C1","phase":"deliberation","remaining_ms":750461,"role_id":"council","turn_number":9}},"isError":false},"server":"aar","tool":"submit_council_vote"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782784299877}]}
